{
  "texts": [
    "[23] demonstrated that using TL within the same domain for medical applications is highly effective.",
    "Furthermore, for medical applications, the performance of the TL-based model has been shown to depend on the similarity between the source and target domains [24] [25] [26] [27] [28].",
    "Alzubaidi et al.",
    "[24] found that using a small number of unlabelled images from the same domain as the target task for TL performs better than using a large number of labelled images from a different domain in medical image applications.",
    "This was tested on two medical tasks, skin and breast cancer."
  ]
}